  <brief_title>Metacognitive Therapy Versus Cognitive Behavioral Therapy for Mixed Anxiety Disorders: A Randomized Controlled Trial.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Metacognitive Therapy Versus Cognitive Behavioral Therapy for Mixed Anxiety Disorders: A Randomized Controlled Trial.</official_title>
